gig_month_str %>% 
  ggplot(data = ., aes(x = time, y = vals*totals, group = times, fill = times)) + 
  geom_col() + 
  #geom_smooth(se = F) + 
  facet_wrap(~app, scales = "free_y") + 
  theme_bw() +
  scale_color_brewer(type = "qual", palette = "Set1") +
  geom_vline(xintercept = 0, linetype = "dashed", color = "red")
